@startuml Fase2_VistaLogica

title Fase 2 - Vista Logica (Containers)

skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam wrapWidth 260
skinparam maxMessageSize 200

actor "Profissional de Saude" as User

rectangle "Simulador Clinico" {
  component "Web SPA\n(SimuladorClinico.Web)" as SPA
  component "API REST\n(SimuladorClinico.Api)" as API
  component "Application Layer\n(ISimulacaoService, DTOs, orquestracao)" as APP
  component "Domain Layer\n(Entidades, Enums, regras)" as DOMAIN
  component "Infrastructure\n(IChatModelService, Knowledge, persistencia)" as INFRA
  database "Sessoes em memoria\nConcurrentDictionary" as STORE
}

cloud "Ollama local\n(mistral:latest)" as LLM
cloud "Python AI Service\n(FastAPI)" as PYAI

User --> SPA : interage com chat e simulacao
SPA --> API : HTTPS JSON
API --> APP : chamadas de casos de uso
APP --> DOMAIN : aplica regras de negocio
APP --> INFRA : resolve dependencias
INFRA --> STORE : guarda as sessoes
INFRA --> LLM : gera resposta do paciente
INFRA ..> PYAI : integracao alternativa / futura

note right of APP
Orquestracao principal da simulacao:
- Iniciar sessao
- Processar mensagem
- Obter estado da sessao
- Concluir e avaliar
end note


@enduml
